<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>20: 2 groups of 10 is 20.</li>
      <li>18: I counted by 2 (2, 4, 6, 8, 10, 12, 14, 16, 18).</li>
      <li>16: I counted by 2 or it’s one group of 2 less than the last equation.</li>
      <li>14: I counted by 2 or it’s one group of 2 less than the last equation.</li>
    </ul>
